<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>A value filtered by Zend_Filter_LocalizedToNormalized includes a decimal separator at the end of the string even though the precision is specified as zero.</p>

<p>Test Case:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$n = '12345.67890';

$filter = new Zend_Filter_LocalizedToNormalized(array('locale' =&gt; 'en_US', 'precision' =&gt; 0));

Zend_Debug::dump($n, 'original');
Zend_Debug::dump($filter-&gt;filter($n), 'filtered');
</code></pre>

<p>Actual Output:</p>

<pre class="literal">
original string(11) "12345.67890"

filtered string(6) "12345."
</pre>

<p>Expected Output:</p>

<pre class="literal">
original string(11) "12345.67890"

filtered string(5) "12345"
</pre>

